      <div class="id-card-sub">Summer 2025</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="projects-wrap">
  <div class="projects-header">
    <div class="eyebrow">Selected Work · 2024–2026</div>
    <h2 class="projects-title">Engineering at the<br><em>hardware–software</em> boundary</h2>
    <p class="projects-sub">Systems where software carries direct physical consequences — built from the register up.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="projects-grid">
    <div class="project-card" onclick="location.href='project-soil.html'">
      <div class="card-visual"><div class="card-visual-bg card-v1"></div><div class="card-circuit"></div><div class="card-icon" style="color:#4f9cf9;">🌱</div><span class="card-status status-active">Active</span></div>
      <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tags"><span class="tag">C</span><span class="tag">Modbus-RTU</span><span class="tag">RS-485</span><span class="tag">Arduino</span></div><div class="card-title">Advanced Soil Sensor System</div><div class="card-desc">Multi-node RS-485 bus polling an NPK sensor via Modbus-RTU, streaming calibrated live readings to an LCD. 88.9% validated accuracy against certified references.</div><div class="card-arrow">View Project →</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card" onclick="location.href='project-maze.html'">
      <div class="card-visual"><div class="card-visual-bg card-v2"></div><div class="card-circuit"></div><div class="card-icon" style="color:#ef4444;">🤖</div><span class="card-status status-complete">Complete</span></div>
      <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tags"><span class="tag">C</span><span class="tag">ATmega32U4</span><span class="tag">PID</span><span class="tag">FSM</span></div><div class="card-title">Autonomous Maze-Solving Robot</div><div class="card-desc">Full embedded stack: PID line-follower, FSM intersection classifier, reflectance sensor driver. Two-run path reduction with real-time OLED debugging.</div><div class="card-arrow">View Project →</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card" onclick="location.href='project-avr.html'">
      <div class="card-visual"><div class="card-visual-bg card-v3"></div><div class="card-circuit"></div><div class="card-icon" style="color:#818cf8;">⚙️</div><span class="card-status status-complete">Complete</span></div>
      <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tags"><span class="tag">AVR Assembly</span><span class="tag">ATmega328P</span></div><div class="card-title">Multi-Precision Arithmetic Engine</div><div class="card-desc">32-bit add/subtract and 32×32→64-bit multiply in hand-written AVR assembly with a stack-based calling convention.</div><div class="card-arrow">View Project →</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card" onclick="location.href='project-signal.html'">
      <div class="card-visual"><div class="card-visual-bg card-v4"></div><div class="card-circuit"></div><div class="card-icon" style="color:#a78bfa;">〰️</div><span class="card-status status-complete">Complete</span></div>
      <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tags"><span class="tag">AVR Assembly</span><span class="tag">AD7302 DAC</span></div><div class="card-title">Programmable Signal Generator</div><div class="card-desc">AVR Assembly firmware driving an AD7302 DAC to produce sine, triangle, square, and sawtooth waveforms with user-programmable frequency.</div><div class="card-arrow">View Project →</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card" onclick="location.href='project-speaker.html'">
      <div class="card-visual"><div class="card-visual-bg card-v5"></div><div class="card-circuit"></div><div class="card-icon" style="color:#7dd3b0;">🎙️</div><span class="card-status status-complete">Complete</span></div>
      <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tags"><span class="tag">MATLAB</span><span class="tag">DSP</span><span class="tag">ML</span></div><div class="card-title">Speaker Recognition System</div><div class="card-desc">100% identification accuracy across 61 test recordings using magnitude spectrogram features, Hamming windowing, and minimum-distance scoring.</div><div class="card-arrow">View Project →</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card" onclick="location.href='project-microscope.html'">
      <div class="card-visual"><div class="card-visual-bg card-v6"></div><div class="card-circuit"></div><div class="card-icon" style="color:#f4a261;">🔬</div><span class="card-status status-complete">Complete</span></div>
      <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tags"><span class="tag">Python</span><span class="tag">Raspberry Pi</span><span class="tag">Computer Vision</span></div><div class="card-title">Calibrated Measurement Microscope</div><div class="card-desc">Python-controlled Raspberry Pi digital microscope with pixel-to-micron spatial calibration and real-time scale bar overlay for PCB inspection.</div><div class="card-arrow">View Project →</div></div>
