      <div class="card-body"><div class="card-tags"><span class="tag">C++</span><span class="tag">OOP</span><span class="tag">CI/CD</span></div><div class="card-title">14-Body Gravitational Simulation</div><div class="card-desc">Solar system simulation in C++ using Singleton, Visitor, Factory, and Prototype patterns. Earth's orbit reproduced with &lt;1,000 km accuracy over 31.5M time steps.</div><div class="card-arrow">View Project →</div></div>
